title: Buffy Season Eight #4 - The Long Way Home - Part Four
description:

The Slayer population of the world has gone from two to nearly two thousand. Almost five hundred are working around the world with Buffy&#039;s organization in squads- or "terrorist cells", according to the American military. Buffy, Xander, Dawn and a passel of slayers are currently bunked out in a Scottish castle, where the latest mission revealed a strange symbol carved into human bodies.
